418
00:30:26,242 --> 00:30:27,952
Corra.

419
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,662
Corra, fuja da Laurel.

420
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:31,997
Corra o mais rápido que puder.

421
00:30:32,206 --> 00:30:34,124
